songs.title: Sucker Punch
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Push and pull me closer
Habit forming, you should stay far away
Colored caffeine magic
Lights my night up
I'm aware of my fate
It's too late

[Chorus]
After all is said and done
I am not the one
I am not the one
After all is said and done
You are still the one
You are still the one

[Verse 2]
Perfect measured pieces
Fit together you and I
Hey bright eyes
Don't deny my weakness
You're the jet and
I'm the stream right behind you
Behind you

[Chorus]
After all is said and done
I am not the one
I am not the one
After all is said and done
You are still the one
You are still the one

[Interlude]

[Chorus]
After all is said and done
I am not the one
I am not the one
After all is said and done
You are still the one
You are still the one
